%p
  The PROIEL and ISWOC treebanks can now be browsed using
  != link_to 'Syntacticus', 'http://syntacticus.org'
  without a username or password. You will also find links to the raw data and documentation there.

%p
  If you have already registered with a username and password here, or you depend on functionality not yet offered by
  != link_to 'Syntacticus', 'http://syntacticus.org'
  you can still log in below. Please note that access to this site will be restricted in 2018 and eventually disabled.

%p
  If you are a treebank annotator, treebank reviewer or treebank administrator, please log in below.

= semantic_form_for resource, :as => resource_name, :url => session_path(resource_name) do |f|
  = f.inputs "Sign in" do
    ._50
      != f.input :login, :label => 'User name'
    ._50
      != f.input :password
    != f.submit "Sign in"
    %br
    != link_to "Register new account", new_registration_path(resource_name)
    %br
    != link_to "Forgot your password?", new_password_path(resource_name)
